#: includes/class-admin.php:32 includes/class-admin.php:33
msgid "DSGVO Webfonts"
msgstr "GDPR Webfonts"

#: includes/class-admin.php:43 includes/class-admin.php:44
msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard"

#: includes/class-admin.php:52 includes/class-admin.php:53
#: includes/class-admin.php:359
msgid "Einstellungen"
msgstr "Settings"

#: includes/class-admin.php:152
msgid "DSGVO Webfonts & externe Anfragen"
msgstr "GDPR Webfonts & External Requests"

#: includes/class-admin.php:156
msgid "Scan abgeschlossen. Die Ergebnisse werden unten angezeigt."
msgstr "Scan complete. Results are shown below."

#: includes/class-admin.php:165
msgid "Scan starten"
msgstr "Start scan"

#: includes/class-admin.php:168
msgid "Scan läuft …"
msgstr "Scanning …"

#: includes/class-admin.php:172
msgid "Scannt alle veröffentlichten Seiten und Beiträge (bis zu 200 URLs)."
msgstr "Scans all published pages and posts (up to 200 URLs)."

#: includes/class-admin.php:174
msgid ""
"Kostenlose Version: scannt die Startseite sowie bis zu 4 zuletzt "
"veröffentlichte Seiten/Beiträge."
msgstr ""
"Free version: scans the homepage and up to 4 most recently published pages/"
"posts."

#: includes/class-admin.php:176
msgid "Mit Pro alle Seiten scannen →"
msgstr "Scan all pages with Pro →"

#: includes/class-admin.php:186
msgid "Noch kein Scan durchgeführt"
msgstr "No scan performed yet"

#: includes/class-admin.php:188
msgid ""
"Klicke auf \"Scan starten\", um das gerenderte HTML deiner Seiten auf "
"externe Anfragen zu prüfen. Das Plugin erkennt Dienste wie Google Fonts, "
"Analytics, YouTube, Gravatar und weitere, die personenbezogene Daten an "
"Dritte übertragen."
msgstr ""
"Click \"Start scan\" to check the rendered HTML of your pages for external "
"requests. The plugin detects services such as Google Fonts, Analytics, "
"YouTube, Gravatar, and others that transmit personal data to third parties."

#: includes/class-admin.php:191 includes/class-admin.php:266
msgid "Hinweis:"
msgstr "Note:"

#: includes/class-admin.php:192 includes/class-admin.php:267
msgid ""
"Statischer Scan des ausgelieferten HTML – per JavaScript dynamisch "
"nachgeladene Anfragen werden ggf. nicht erkannt. Ersetzt keine "
"Rechtsberatung."
msgstr ""
"Static scan of the delivered HTML – requests loaded dynamically via "
"JavaScript may not be detected. Not a substitute for legal advice."

#: includes/class-admin.php:229
#, php-format
msgid "Gesamtrisiko: %s"
msgstr "Overall risk: %s"

#: includes/class-admin.php:238
#, php-format
msgid "%d externer Dienst(e)"
msgstr "%d external service(s)"

#: includes/class-admin.php:247
#, php-format
msgid "%d externe Anfrage(n)"
msgstr "%d external request(s)"

#: includes/class-admin.php:257
#, php-format
msgid "Gescannt am: %s"
msgstr "Scanned on: %s"

#: includes/class-admin.php:272
msgid ""
"Keine externen Anfragen erkannt. Bitte prüfe dennoch manuell, ob JavaScript-"
"basierte Anfragen vorliegen."
msgstr ""
"No external requests detected. Please still check manually for JavaScript-"
"based requests."

#: includes/class-admin.php:275
msgid "Erkannte externe Dienste"
msgstr "Detected external services"

#: includes/class-admin.php:299
#, php-format
msgid "%d Anfrage(n)"
msgstr "%d request(s)"

#: includes/class-admin.php:308
msgid "Empfehlung:"
msgstr "Recommendation:"

#: includes/class-admin.php:314
msgid "Beispiel-URLs anzeigen"
msgstr "Show example URLs"

#: includes/class-admin.php:333
msgid "Schnell-Maßnahmen"
msgstr "Quick actions"

#: includes/class-admin.php:335
msgid ""
"Einige häufige Anfragen kannst du direkt über die Plugin-Einstellungen "
"deaktivieren oder lokal ersetzen."
msgstr ""
"Some common requests can be disabled or replaced locally directly via the "
"plugin settings."

#: includes/class-admin.php:337
msgid "Zu den Einstellungen"
msgstr "Go to settings"

#: includes/class-admin.php:363
msgid "Einstellungen gespeichert."
msgstr "Settings saved."

#: includes/class-admin.php:368
msgid "Kostenlose Version"
msgstr "Free version"

#: includes/class-admin.php:370
msgid ""
"Die kostenlose Version scannt die Startseite sowie bis zu 4 zuletzt "
"veröffentlichte Seiten/Beiträge und bietet grundlegende Schnell-Maßnahmen "
"für häufige DSGVO-Probleme."
msgstr ""
"The free version scans the homepage and up to 4 most recently published "
"pages/posts and provides basic quick actions for common GDPR issues."

#: includes/class-admin.php:381
msgid "Google Fonts entfernen"
msgstr "Remove Google Fonts"

#: includes/class-admin.php:387
msgid "Google Fonts entfernen (extern → keine Anfrage an Google)"
msgstr "Remove Google Fonts (external → no request to Google)"

#: includes/class-admin.php:390
msgid ""
"Entfernt alle externen Google-Fonts-Anfragen aus dem HTML (<link>-Tags, "
"@import). Stelle sicher, dass du die Schriften lokal hostest oder andere "
"Schriften verwendest."
msgstr ""
"Removes all external Google Fonts requests from the HTML (<link> tags, "
"@import). Make sure you host the fonts locally or use alternative fonts."

#: includes/class-admin.php:396
msgid "WordPress-Emojis deaktivieren"
msgstr "Disable WordPress emojis"

#: includes/class-admin.php:402
msgid "WordPress-Emojis deaktivieren (entfernt s.w.org-Anfrage)"
msgstr "Disable WordPress emojis (removes s.w.org request)"

#: includes/class-admin.php:405
msgid ""
"WordPress lädt standardmäßig Emoji-Skripte von s.w.org. Diese Option "
"deaktiviert dieses Verhalten vollständig."
msgstr ""
"WordPress loads emoji scripts from s.w.org by default. This option "
"disables that behavior entirely."

#: includes/class-admin.php:411
msgid "Gravatar lokal ersetzen"
msgstr "Replace Gravatar locally"

#: includes/class-admin.php:417
msgid "Gravatar lokal ersetzen (keine Anfrage an gravatar.com)"
msgstr "Replace Gravatar locally (no request to gravatar.com)"

#: includes/class-admin.php:420
msgid ""
"Ersetzt alle Gravatar-Anfragen durch einen lokalen SVG-Platzhalter-Avatar. "
"Kein externer Request an gravatar.com."
msgstr ""
"Replaces all Gravatar requests with a local SVG placeholder avatar. "
"No external request to gravatar.com."

#: includes/class-admin.php:426
msgid "Einstellungen speichern"
msgstr "Save settings"

#: includes/class-admin.php:431
msgid "DSGVO Webfonts Pro"
msgstr "GDPR Webfonts Pro"

#: includes/class-admin.php:435
msgid "Google Fonts automatisch lokal hosten (Schriften bleiben erhalten)"
msgstr "Automatically host Google Fonts locally (fonts are preserved)"

#: includes/class-admin.php:439
msgid ""
"Externe Einbettungen lokalisieren: YouTube (nocookie), Google Maps & Vimeo "
"als Klick-zum-Laden-Platzhalter"
msgstr ""
"Localize external embeds: YouTube (nocookie), Google Maps & Vimeo as "
"click-to-load placeholder"

#: includes/class-admin.php:443
msgid "Geplanter automatischer Re-Scan + E-Mail-Bericht"
msgstr "Scheduled automatic re-scan + email report"

#: includes/class-admin.php:447
msgid "Multisite-Unterstützung"
msgstr "Multisite support"

#: includes/class-admin.php:451
msgid "PDF-Konformitätsbericht"
msgstr "PDF compliance report"

#: includes/class-admin.php:456
